captions.text:
There they are, this year's tributes and
what a fine bunch they are.
Somebody help us! This hurts really bad!!

Well, it appears the odds aren't in
their favor..
I don't wanna play this game!
(ahhh) What an exciting Hunger Games, children are murdering each other left and right
Wh- What is this? District 9 has found the mech suit!
Two tributes from the same district!

There is a slight rule change
regarding our previous rule change.
The uh, previous rule change has been revoked.
Uh, there can only be one, so, uh..
Yea, it's too late. We already won, you can't change the rules after the game is over!
Um, you'll just have to kill each other..
Now ehh fight to the death!
Eh, it doesn't work like that.
Now less talking and more killing each other
What if we refuse to kill each other?
Yea, what do you think about that?
Just... fight to the death please.

We would rather commit suicide than
kill each other.
and you wouldn't let us do that.
You must have a victor, right?
That's right, we'll pull a Romeo and Juliet 'cause we're in love!!
Because we are sooooo in love.

And we're gonna eat these berries if you
don't let us both win.
Ok! You got me, I don't really love him.
He, he's a nice guy a nice guy and all but I'm not gonna commit suicide over it.
I mean, have you seen Gale???

Hey you guys ever think we should use
all this money and technology to actually
End world hunger?... Save the rain forest?..
Would rather, uhh, kids fight to the death??
